'''Amadou Mbow''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Senegali|Senegal]]<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm10641642/</ref> .  Azwi cyane ku ruhare nka 'Issa' muri filime y’ikinamico ndengakamere ''Atlantics'' <ref>https://www.iwmbuzz.com/tag/amadou-mbow-as-issa</ref>.  Usibye kuba umukinnyi, anashushanya ibishushanyo mbonera kandi akunda amafoto<ref>https://www.advitamdistribution.com/films/atlantique/</ref>.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye kandi akurira i Dakar, muri [[Senegali]] . 

Umuhungu wumucuzi wa [[Senegali]] ukomoka muri Fulani ukomoka i Futa, Amadou Mbow numuhungu wa nyina na murumuna wa bashiki be batatu<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/337570079_Characterization_and_Analysis_of_the_Socio-Economic_Issues_of_Ziguinchor_Urban_Livestock_in_Senegal</ref>.  Mu myaka ye y'ubwangavu, basketball yari ifite umwanya wingenzi mubuzima bwe. Nyuma yimyaka itari mike akora imyitozo muri DUC ( Dakar University Club ) imwemerera kongera ubumenyi, reaction ndetse no kwiyemeza. Amaherezo yahisemo kureka siporo kugirango arusheho gushimishwa nisi yerekana amajwi yimenyereza nkumuntu wiyigisha<ref>http://uam.sn/universite-amadou-mahtar-mbow-de-dakar-uam</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2019, Mbow yatoranijwe muri firime ''Atlantics'' iyobowe na Mati Diop nka firime ye ya mbere<ref>https://www.screendaily.com/features/frances-cesar-academy-facing-calls-for-shake-up-over-transparency-diversity-and-polanski/5146792.article</ref>.  Muri iyo filime, yakinnye nk'umupolisi ukiri muto 'Issa' woherejwe gukora iperereza ku muriro udasanzwe utwika mu buriri bwa Ada mu ijoro ry'ubukwe bwe<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=871618.html</ref>. Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere mu murwa mukuru wa Dakar mbere yuko isohoka muri [[Senegali]]<ref>http://uam.sn/universite-amadou-mahtar-mbow-de-dakar-uam</ref>. Filime yari ifite ibitekerezo byiza cyane kubayinenga kandi yerekanwe mubirori byinshi bya firime. Filime yaje gutsindira igihembo cya Grand Prix mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2019<ref>https://www.festival-cannes.com/en/artist/amadou-mbow</ref> . Muri 2020, Amadou Mbow yatoranijwe muri Césars 2020 mubyiciro bya "Ibyahishuwe"<ref>https://www.alamy.com/amadou-mbow-attending-the-cesar-revelations-2020-photocall-at-the-petit-palais-in-paris-france-on-january-13-2020-photo-by-aurore-marechalabacapresscom-image387867261.html</ref>. 

